text: Ernie Fischer (July 12, 1930 - April 20, 2019) was an American wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle welterweight at the 1956 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2019 deaths Category:American male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United States Category:Wrestlers at the 1956 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Baltimore
